a:50:{i:1273959;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273959";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"291";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:170:"well... ive wanted to interract with starlit, but sharp is even less of a mindreader than shard. he&#039;s unaware of her interest in him.. unless that&#039;s changed... ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766144";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6d00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247661429";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#9000b0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273960;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273960";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:4:"text";s:186:"I mean, he&#039;s...very standoffish and he&#039;s in a waspnest. That&#039;s just what it is...he was useful when the robbery happened, that&#039;s good, he&#039;s not inconsequential. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766158";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247661551";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273961;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273961";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:4:"text";s:164:"Well Starlit is dumb. I made her in two seconds because I wanted to help Chanterelle&#039;s event succeed. Obviously it didn&#039;t need me much, but I was trying. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766190";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247661876";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273963;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273963";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"291";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:541:"im kind of stuck in character, though... sharp is a severe man, he&#039;s a noble that comes from a time when the nobility tended to be the most dangerous warriors on the battlefield, and led the charge, personally, and were first in battle. he&#039;s not a noble that bought his way in with money, he won it through the leadership of his people, so he&#039;s only interested in economy from the perspective of the health of his small mountain state, whreas the toehrs seem to be in it for personal profit. this has already put him at odds..";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766270";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6d00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247662687";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#9000b0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273964;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273964";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:4:"text";s:33:"Sharp is, at least, interesting. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766275";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247662724";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273966;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273966";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"291";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:271:"and i like starlit, im honestly more itnerested in her than i am in acrux or wintermane.. wintermane seems empty, just a name, and acrux is just.. &quot;joe but in the past&quot; hes a carbon copy... starlit interests me more, to know more about where Sapphire came from.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766308";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6d00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247663063";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#9000b0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273971;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273971";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:4:"text";s:396:"I think if you really want ponies to interact with you more you should make a character that&#039;s just throwaway happy. Not super smart, not a noble...just a funloving pony. A happy mare with a happy job that can go around being happy. Easily accessible, outgoing...etc. You know? Keep Shard as your mane, but sometimes just be silly. Discord is good, but he can&#039;t be around all the time. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766430";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247664271";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273972;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273972";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:4:"text";s:60:"Oh...well, you guessed she was Sapphire&#039;s ancestor eh? ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766448";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247664454";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273973;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273973";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"291";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:102:"XP not much of a leap. theyre both caleld Night, they&#039;re both somewhat dreamy and detached.. heh.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424766491";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6d00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247664895";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#9000b0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273974;a:14:{s:11:"chat_l